Package: ssTA
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-15-06
Title: Shape Space Trait Association
Authors: c(person("Chris", "Anderson", email = christopher_anderson@urmc.rochester.edu),
			person("William", "Bender", email = william_bender@urmc.rochester.edu))
Maintainer: William Bender <william_bender@urmc.rochester.edu>
Description: aligns Amino Acid sequences, creates a distance matrix of antigenic distance between sequences, performs multidimensional scaling on the distance matrix, and performs statistical test for association between a trait and the distance matrix.
